<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink348">
<l>avarō vārār tāṉvan taṉṟē</l>
<l>valañcuri marāam vēyntunam</l>
<l>maṇaṅkamaḻ taṇpoḻiṉ malarum poḻutē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Won’t he himself come? The season has arrived,</l>
<l>when mightily twisted Marām tree is covered with [flowers], </l>
<l>and our cool fragrance-emitting grove blooms.   </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
